-------------------------------
* How to get ROM ?
-------------------------------

** Download SDK

	Access to above official page, and go to
	 - "Design & Development"
	  - "R-Car S4 SDK for gateway"
	   - "Software Downloads"

	NOTE. v3.16.0 case

	 - R-Car S4 SDK Linux PKG with GCC compiler v3.16.0

** Prepare items

	NOTE. v3.16.0 case

	Binary
	 - xOS3_SDK1_Linux_ReferenceSDK1_v3.16.0_release/rcar-xos/v3.16.0/os/bootloader/s4/s4sk/

-------------------------------
* How to know the Ether Mac address
-------------------------------

	You need to use "R-Car S4 Starter Kit Configuration Tool" to
	know the Ether Mac address.

	You can get it from
	- above "Official Page"
	 - "Software Downloads"
	  - "R-Car S4 Starter Kit Configuration Tool"

	Run "S4_StarterKit_Configurationr.exe" on Windows.

